rComments: Structure and function of the nucleus. I really enjoyed Dr. Palazzo's lectures. He is also really interesting to talk to. I like that he focuses on conceptual understanding as opposed to rote memorization. Understanding systems as opposed to memorizing them (but you will still have to memorize, as this is biochem :D). Good prof.
